Alice's Room, Sagamore Hill national historic site

As the eldest child, Alice Lee Roosevelt always had her own room and did not compete with her siblings for space. Her room is furnished with a bedroom set that had belonged to her mother, Alice Hathaway Lee Roosevelt.
